name: CHANGE
description:
Insights from the Dreaming Pool - There is magic in Change. Alchemy and transmutation.

Change is occurring all of the time. There is only change from one moment to the next. Sometimes in life big changes come along. We might resist prolonging the shift, holding it off, running away, and ignoring it because we’re afraid. It will come and get you one way or the other so turn and face it, relax your muscles and take one step at a
time. Trust me it’ll be worth it... 

The Dreaming Pool Oracle is a collaboration between artists Maia Mellier 🕸 🕷 (@maiamellier) & AEVIN (@aevin_io)
